title: The Seafarers - The Atlantic Crossing - Melvin Maddocks.epub
description:
PUB. Presents a history of navigation and shipping across the Atlantic to America beginning with the Mayflower.
There is no Bibliography, Acknowledgements, Picture Credits or Index. A lot of pictures were spread across two pages, they are not included, other pictures have been moved to the end of the chapter they were in.
Thanks to STBGD for the PDF upload.
